{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef621bdd3b","title":"曾清泾批斗会（或辩论会）记录稿","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d889fea46","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":9,"articleId":"ef621bdd3b"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9e60fc8c1b","type":"title","text":"曾清泾批斗会（或辩论会）记录稿","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"25a7364ba3","type":"paragraph","text":"[曾清泾即曾清经，西南师范学院化学系58级学生右派，是四川省不予“改正”的21名右派之一（重庆市第一名）。本数据库有他两篇文章《几点政治见解》、《致毛主席和党中央首长的信》。]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7376ff96c8","type":"paragraph","text":"7月9日（1957年）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"64060a401e","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：两天来的思想活动、检查情况：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"19d57fdd9b","type":"paragraph","text":"大会前，对言论的严重性认识不够，是在未认识清楚之情况下说出的，这些言论若让敌人知道是会拉过去的。经过大会使我从梦中警醒，我得感谢大家。因此，当天下午就进行了检讨，检查自己言论为什么错误，及考虑未交待清楚的地方。对大会意见作了思考，看是否必须回答。下午写了一个多钟头，当时对如何写检讨或还有点摸不到底，同学们告诉我必须找出原始思想，自己是否立场问题，对土改是否有认识。星期日仍检查思想，按照言论等的秩序进行，共提出八个问题，以找出原始思想，也查了现在的认识。昨天本欲与日光报社联系，提出五十多个问题，找出了原始思想和目的，准备发表，自己的认识批判也用来发表。下午，康俊看了我的检查，认为不解决问题，故而又改变方式，找出系统，但仍不解决问题，故有另写出自己的认识批判，康看后认为未解决问题，并认为还不深刻，必须在班上谈出，加以批判，使认识更深刻，故未能去发表。自己思想上毒害是很深的，故认识还很不深刻，希望大家多帮助。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"87dbc0cd3f","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：发表目的何在？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"276654c9a7","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：大会要求检查，为满足大家的要求，使大家了解我，故仅管不成熟的可发表。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4bf9776ae7","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：为满足同学要求还是自己检查思想？在以上谈话中并未谈出思想活动，也为谈出原始思想为什么？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"722b4561e3","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：只谈了过程，主要之要谈出自己思想的活动。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"a79ecb0f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"康：到底是什么指导思想指导你在进行检查？到底有什么样的思想活动？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"6d3802ad05","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：开会下来，见自己已走到很危险的道路上，但自己不知道，以至谈出了哪些话，一直认为以前的是正确的，会后才知道自己很坏。以前的检查都不对，未找出正确的立场，必须再检查。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"e2684f9270","type":"paragraph","text":"再有，若抗拒检查，则自己没有挽救，到现在，一直在找方法去认识自己对党的仇恨在哪里？必须检查，否则是不能挽救的。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"0b87b0342c","type":"paragraph","text":"现在感到自己头脑很重，决不能放松检查，现在思想一直是很严重的，这样就考虑到一方面，……并未感到是同学的逼迫，只有检查清楚，与大家认识一致才好。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"5859a13f03","type":"paragraph","text":"康：最现实的还可挽救？是什么？思想沉重的表现？为什么在大会后？从哪些具体事实才感到自己是坏的？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"9f28889a44","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：现实的感觉是食堂工友说过，若不检查就停止伙食。站到敌人方面去了就没有出路。一个右派分子就可能走到反革命的道路上去。自己在面临解放时，还参加自卫队，这就是个反动的组织，但自己一直没有重视。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7ee59c0cea","type":"paragraph","text":"关于家庭的事自己知道很少，在大会上说出来了，自己才知道我家庭并不是很清淡的。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"2b41aa0a12","type":"paragraph","text":"沉重是在于，以前是一涌而入出了口，发言很成熟，但现在是逆水推舟，不能很好的认识。不知到底是为什么，因此说不出个所以然，故此沉重。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"d4c8872eb5","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：思想沉重并感到非检查不可，是否因“不准吃饭”*要你回应？","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"b4d48f27d2","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：不影响，最主要的还是自己想认识而认识不出来。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"fbe6c24cce","type":"paragraph","text":"康：建议写信感到警（惊）慌是为什么？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ee7050b6b2","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：我还是同意写信回去，但想到回去后是否还要（？）走，故而顾虑。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ad416532fa","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：假使给你定了伙食，不让你回去劳改，是否还要检查？","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ddd95f47d4","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：不是这个问题，原有错误思想，但认识不到才感到沉重。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"b2e4f8a275","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：但为何在未找出以上问题前不感到沉重？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4cc1428f68","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：因以前未认识到自己言论的严重性。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"31e2340746","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：你如何交待鸣放以来的思想动态？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"685d04a103","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：表现在哪些地方？","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"b6bd73cd90","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：原来清楚的了解从哪些地方向党进攻，但我并不是那样的人，并不是清清楚楚的，现在感到讲不出来，因为思想上没有那些东西。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"a10a8dbb00","type":"paragraph","text":"康：那你直到现在还认为是信口开河了？","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"9c29a3bad3","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：事实上绝不可能是冲（脱）口而出的。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"67ffa48824","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：没有一个系统的东西支配你，怎样一涌而入呢？支配你一涌而入者到底是什么？你一涌而入不是一次，而之前发言7次，各次说法不同，但总的思想是一个，那到底是什么支配的呢？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"845551a4bc","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：认识不到可以帮助，但原始思想只有自己知道。这样大个事情没有动机、目的是不可能的？","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"97c5624c31","type":"paragraph","text":"郑：这两天来到底是如何想的？是愿不愿谈出自己原始思想的问题。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1ad8321b84","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：自大会以来，检查了思想，一直考虑最初为何要这样谈，目的是什么？","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7766a19b22","type":"paragraph","text":"说怕再说出来，免得搞大了，是指给毛主席的信写后，是想到国民党回来后对我好些，就快活些了。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"bad46f763d","type":"paragraph","text":"说台湾是中国的，而不是共产党的，这是蒋介石的（中国不是*共产党）的反映，是相当反动的。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"09104d67d9","type":"paragraph","text":"说搞大了是发表了那些没有谈过的。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"2f031e4fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"我知道那些都是辨不倒的（在说之是即如此想法），党听取意见，认为可行就能达到。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"88fa9f4b8a","type":"paragraph","text":"若谈到原始思想，则可能有两种情况，一是作为人民内部矛盾，一是更加愤怒，非把你赶走，非把你处死不可。最可能的还是前一种。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"fbb849bacb","type":"paragraph","text":"在最初的时候，关于不要共产党领导的问题，心里还是很怕的。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"dbf01f3bc1","type":"paragraph","text":"现在的行动和最初的是有些距离的，最初仅是自己的想法，要求国民党回来，对党很不满，要推翻他。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"e5bee995d8","type":"paragraph","text":"康：既是人民内部矛盾问题，你怎样来认识那些问题？","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"0711a8482b","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：看《钢铁战士》后，与同学交换意见，我想我发言结果是和很恶毒的，那些事原来就那样想的。昨天就在检查，自己还是有顾虑，我一直相信党仍是作为内部矛盾处理，但同学们都要看，就有顾虑，怕引起同学的愤怒。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"53a2df8bdb","type":"paragraph","text":"并不想避免同学的愤怒，仍想*是表露得真实，但并不是在措词上打转。群众愤怒不愤怒，并不看措词如何，而是看如何认识正确，解决问题，但现在我不怕愤怒。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"72922c0658","type":"paragraph","text":"现在准备在班上来检查自己。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"2a1ad549b2","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：以人民内部矛盾处理，你认为应怎样除去毒草呢？群众之愤怒是在于你没有彻底交待。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"cc583367bf","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：那就只有真实的交待自己。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"fdfe5807d6","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：说出那些话一定有个思想支配。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"aa54dc4259","type":"paragraph","text":"曾老师：应了解同学之愤怒在于发出反动言论后，并不老实检查自己，要同学不愤怒，首先自己态度应端正起来，老实交待。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"11a68f61d9","type":"paragraph","text":"陈、刘：若不真实的交待你自己的原始思想，不说你怎样进行检讨，就会引起同学愤怒。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"8067a60fc2","type":"paragraph","text":"贺：要想蒙混过关，作表面的检查，就会引起愤怒，若不老实交待，也许就不会作为内部矛盾处理了。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"60eec81d76","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：以前的几次检查是空洞的，我自己也知道。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ad7c5ff28d","type":"paragraph","text":"康：什么叫原始思想？","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1cf88407cc","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：原来讲了话，觉得心里痛快，这就是原始思想。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4ca7e97336","type":"paragraph","text":"要国民党回来的说法是有目的的，就是想要他回来给我撑腰。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7993cdb423","type":"paragraph","text":"班上处理不好，要大家了解，这也是目的，使关系改善。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"f1fda214cc","type":"paragraph","text":"讲那些话是有目的的，其结果是要求达到取消党，要国民党回来给我撑腰。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1dd5a4c75f","type":"paragraph","text":"寸、刘：为什么要说：**……我坚决反党反社会主义？","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"c1e1f129a8","type":"paragraph","text":"康：你是否感到有些胜利了，班级关系改变了？","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ce980107a0","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：你是发牢骚还是别有用心，有目的？","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7740017fe5","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：如何达到反对党的目的的？","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"129aa12964","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：第一次发言是发牢骚，以后就是要取消党。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"79f9722a99","type":"paragraph","text":"康、寸：第一次就谈到政治压迫、经济压迫，并谈到赞成资——，是发牢骚吗？","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"f1a78b2075","type":"paragraph","text":"为何*开始不谈，要在鸣放时发，而其结果又不是呢？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"2af22f7edd","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：最初是发牢骚，以后就转移了。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"7f1b517d92","type":"paragraph","text":"发牢骚作为试探，以后就一连串的把反对党，取消党的全说出来了，不是信口开河。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"9e407e1944","type":"paragraph","text":"康：支持你的发牢骚为试探，然后反对党的总的支配是什么？","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"22b66344e5","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：其目的就是反党，取消党，希望国民党回来复辟旧社会，因为不满意现在的生活。在旧社会，像我这种人是过得好的，在现社会，只有工农才幸福，其他是不幸福的。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"dee2344421","type":"paragraph","text":"曾老师：为什么现在才谈？","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"8e5fdcdb37","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：因为这两学期班上对我很不好，鸣放又恰是时候，于是利用这个机会，推翻的方法是旧社会复辟。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"27b5fb5ab3","type":"paragraph","text":"不满足，班上对我不好，瞧不起，没有达到我过去的生活，家庭弄得那样惨。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"baf334f808","type":"paragraph","text":"自解放以来就瞧不起。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"3774909c6e","type":"paragraph","text":"思想根源是与反动派靠得很近，解放后一切都推翻了。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"51cb0dc8ed","type":"paragraph","text":"一切好的光荣的是都铲除了，现在都不光荣了。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4e57136b99","type":"paragraph","text":"康：再明确谈谈目的。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"aebc1e97d4","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：最初的目的是改造这环境，取消党，把适合我的环境拿出来。现在这个社会制度对我不好，我要推翻他。旧的制度是很好的适合我的。这是解放以来就有的想法，不是偶然想的。为此，在鸣放中机会到了，逐步达到（最先试探一下，然后放）。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"08fdace54a","type":"paragraph","text":"曾老师：放出来可能不是恢复个人的生活吗？","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"701f5fcc62","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：放的最重要问题是解放台湾问题，这样国民党就轻脚轻手回来，达到复辟的目的。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"877008c286","type":"paragraph","text":"并不想取得联系，因为他们，如右派分子的力量是太小了，主要的力量是台湾，里应外合也必须得到党的同意。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"aea05fc49e","type":"paragraph","text":"要达到自己的目的，就要谈，让大家同意。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4bd3882665","type":"paragraph","text":"工作步骤就是要争取群众相信，这是主要的步骤。争取群众相信的办法是写了广播稿（关于董时光）。其他步骤如民主党的问题，把民主党派与党的关系说的很不好，把国民党说的很好，说的很进步，以争取那些觉悟程度不够的。把土改讲得一团糟，争取地主家庭出身者。把愿接受我领导的青年组织起来，才有力量与其他党派对抗，恢复国民党也是个力量。民主党派没有共产党坚定，它发展起来就等于成（立）组织，其它党都一样，它不是工人阶级，应该为它本阶级利益奋斗，走资本主义。等他们发展大了力量就大了，就是取消共产党的力量。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"4a4634c245","type":"paragraph","text":"有些工人还是不欢迎共产党的（少数），他既然不相信马列主义，我们就要他，以分化工人阶级的力量。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"3b5fa2004a","type":"appellation","text":"《……》（笔者注：应该是一篇文章的题目）这就达到使其他阶级的人民反对工人阶级专政，即从政权方面来反对。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"3a81bc0554","type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义是指导党的，马列主义不尽（近）人情，当然党就不尽（近）人情，不使其成为思想信仰，是取消思想武器，以三民主义、大同思想代替。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"256009b3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"在过去之所以不谈，是因为要取得信任，要有工作。取得我要求的东西，结果没有满足，当然就更仇恨了。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1f46af9a6a","type":"appellation","text":"就整个而言是系统的，从四面八方进行的。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"97a272fec7","type":"subtitle","text":"7月9日 下午","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"06e914ca16","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：原来没有那些办法，只是自解放以来，对党的情绪就是有的，但直到升大学时都很淡，到大学后才不同了。在鸣放时，也并未清楚的找到进攻的手段。","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"6c0abef59b","type":"paragraph","text":"康：如关于台湾问题，就不是现在才想到的，在去年纪念孙中山的时候，你就认为把柄来了。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"0c34aa535f","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：仇恨这个社会也是在这次鸣放中，对照起来，才更仇恨的，以前并没有这个打算。思想基础是有的，即仇恨这个社会，仇恨党，再加以过去有那些思想观点，在鸣放中见大家提的还对，就产生了这些想法。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"d234ce571d","type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得鸣放以前没有什么打算，也没有什么办法的。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"0dc27965dd","type":"paragraph","text":"这个问题必须从实际出发才能解决，如土改时，并没有“以后来推翻你”的打算。","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"d3841d94c5","type":"paragraph","text":"不仅是不满，而是仇恨。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"341bba4b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"康：你是否怕说**说是立场问题。","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"6296ddc150","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：当然是立场问题，是站在反动的，地主阶级的立场走了，地主阶级的立场是与国民党反动派的立场一致的。","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1351a910fa","type":"paragraph","text":"在鸣放前是一贯对党不满，所以才在鸣放中提那些来攻击党，但并不是原已想到，现在才拿出来的。","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"c067dc1248","type":"paragraph","text":"寸、康、江：不真实，如土改问题不可能在现在才想到，不容协商。","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"f35b9e056e","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：却是现在想到的，那些情况是我在家中经过的，就是说思想基础是那时产生的。","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"599f713d62","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：不满意党是早就有的。","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"c3f4abd899","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：是。","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"39e5bf08c6","type":"paragraph","text":"康：除对党的仇恨以外，都是鸣放时想到的，或者是原有些打算？","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"f6cdb47da7","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：以前所有什么打算，对国民党的感情是解放前就有的。","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"bb02910358","type":"paragraph","text":"纪念孙中山是，没有什么不满意的。","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"d88c047253","type":"paragraph","text":"郑：难道是这次才想到？自己没有过组织生活的吗？","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"57f2cf4e84","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：一切打算都是这次想到的，以往只是有些不满。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"91598dcf2c","type":"paragraph","text":"争取群众的办法只是在班上谈谈，在下面没有谈过，最重要的办法就是得到毛主席的同意，引起各民主党派的不满。","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"583be70b52","type":"paragraph","text":"6.8日中午到地理系一年级（桃园五楼）去过。","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ab1d64f0d8","type":"paragraph","text":"讲话后，是和个别同学扯过，但不是争取，并不是主动争取拉拢他。","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"d78ccf99d4","type":"paragraph","text":"康：据你说，全是你一个人跳，那怎么争取群众呢？","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"b8bd36f67f","type":"paragraph","text":"寸：在这种轰轰烈烈的运动中，有关运动的动态等，都不与同学谈吗？","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"330b6a7270","type":"paragraph","text":"曾：我与杨少之玩过多次，但并没有谈过什么，这可去问杨少之（？）。","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"bee41b89ff","type":"paragraph","text":"争取群众另外并没有什么办法，如和熊贵志谈“公式”问题并没有争取的目的。","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"6c142793f3","type":"paragraph","text":"一次和**一起玩（人民日报社论发表后），他说过，以前有些言论是损害党的，我就说，工农是从根本利益上拥护党的。报上这些（？），在资本主义国家看来，就有损于国家的威信。在社论发表前的记不得了。","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"99c10370d2","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣放以前，我认为人民日报是不完全相信的，这是在听了张院长报告以后。","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"1f9632604a","type":"paragraph","text":"据我记得与杨少之要了两次","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"a83e72d50c","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣放中","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ce6b41a814","type":"paragraph","text":"首先是把家庭的情况拉出，取得别人的同情，拉些压迫表明自己是受欺压的，以取得同情，争取群众，这是一方面。","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"07c361cb3f","type":"subtitle","text":"还有就是尽量把国民党说得很好，争取群众造成（对现实不满意）。","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"ad39a69cf5","type":"appellation","text":"曾：记得清楚的就是以上那些。","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"},{"id":"e923be2040","type":"paragraph","text":"希望下去在考虑，肯定不止那些：1.鸣放中如何争取群众 [下中断了]","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b"}],"page":{"id":"6df18077c3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ef621bdd3b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}